title: Internet Information Server 7 (IIS 7) using Windows 2008 Server
description:
This is a full training about configuring, securing and deploying IIS 7 using windows 2008 Server by K-Alliance.

My purpose to share the training is only for educational purposes.... If you like the training then you should contribute to the author and the company by purchasing it or its license so that they will be motivated to create more great training in future to fulfill our learning hunger.

Download, learn, enjoy and purchase.


Thanx to TPB for providing such a great platform for file sharing.....
